cast.original_title: Birds of Prey (and the Fantabulous Emancipation of One Harley Quinn)
cast.overview: Harley Quinn joins forces with a singer, an assassin and a police detective to help a young girl who had a hit placed on her after she stole a rare diamond from a crime lord.
cast.title: Birds of Prey (and the Fantabulous Emancipation of One Harley Quinn)

details.biography: Brandon Garic Notch was born 1979 in the city of Saint Paul Minnesota, but he currently calls the sunny California mountains his home. Brandon is an independent artist, storyteller, actor, writer, tattooist, philanthropist, member of San Bernardino Masonic Lodge number 178, and a 32nd degree Scottish Rite Freemason. Brandon is an accomplished artist internationally recognized and well-known in the tattoo industry, with interests in philosophy, nature, art, science, and consciousness studies.
details.name: Brandon Garic Notch
